1
00:00:44,380 --> 00:00:46,340
=Stealing Heart=

2
00:00:46,700 --> 00:00:48,020
=Episode 9=
(Intoxicated)

3
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:52,310
This is fine deer blood wine.

4
00:00:53,520 --> 00:00:55,109
That would be enough for you.

5
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:06,229
Mrs. Lu.

6
00:01:07,942 --> 00:01:09,270
Mrs. Lu

7
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:12,550
actually chose

8
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:15,030
Lu Siyan's office.

9
00:01:18,359 --> 00:01:20,229
What a gift.

10
00:01:21,159 --> 00:01:22,910
How can I let you down?

11
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,830
(Aphrodisiac incense?)

12
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:32,120
Madam, you have two plans ready.

13
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:34,509
Not only did you prepare deer blood wine
for Chief Shen,

14
00:02:34,509 --> 00:02:36,750
but you also prepared
aphrodisiac incense for Ms. Chuning.

15
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:39,109
I believe both of them
will enjoy a wonderful time.

16
00:02:39,719 --> 00:02:40,590
Come on.

17
00:02:41,159 --> 00:02:42,989
Let's invite the Master for a show.

18
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:43,949
Yes, Madam.

19
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,710
Siyan.

20
00:03:52,348 --> 00:03:53,438
Lin Chuning,

21
00:03:53,439 --> 00:03:54,470
don't come near me.

22
00:03:54,479 --> 00:03:55,359
Get out.

23
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,150
Siyan,

24
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:57,989
did you ask for me?

25
00:03:58,479 --> 00:03:59,198
I didn't.

26
00:03:59,199 --> 00:04:00,310
Leave now.

27
00:04:04,319 --> 00:04:05,190
No.

28
00:04:05,759 --> 00:04:06,949
It's aphrodisiac incense.

29
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:09,959
Siyan,

30
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:10,789
are you okay?

31
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,816
I said get out. Go.

32
00:04:12,817 --> 00:04:14,470
Just go.

33
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,789
Are you okay?

34
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,869
Lin Chuning,

35
00:04:33,251 --> 00:04:34,719
I told you to leave.

36
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:35,869
Siyan.

37
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:39,150
Let go of me.

38
00:04:44,959 --> 00:04:47,950
I saw Gao Yunfeng drag Chuning
into the office.

39
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,958
I'm afraid he might hurt her

40
00:04:49,959 --> 00:04:51,150
out of spite.

41
00:04:52,319 --> 00:04:53,278
Where's Siyan?

42
00:04:53,279 --> 00:04:54,869
I've sent someone to look for him.

43
00:05:10,279 --> 00:05:11,398
Are you insane?

44
00:05:11,399 --> 00:05:12,549
Yes, I am.

45
00:05:12,759 --> 00:05:13,799
Lin Chuning.

46
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,359
You...

47
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,518
Let go of me.

48
00:05:15,519 --> 00:05:17,270
I can't control myself.

49
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,549
I can't.

50
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,150
Lu Siyan.

51
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,030
Lu Siyan.

52
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:22,559
Lu Siyan.

53
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:23,749
Wake up.

54
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:24,950
Lu Siyan.

55
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,549
They want to witness an affair,
don't they?

56
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,159
Then let them.

57
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,749
That way,

58
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:33,350
you'll never be with anyone else.

59
00:05:34,199 --> 00:05:35,309
Lu Siyan,

60
00:05:35,577 --> 00:05:36,950
let go of me.

61
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,629
Let go.

62
00:05:40,811 --> 00:05:45,292
♪I thought the person I loved♪

63
00:05:45,594 --> 00:05:49,104
♪Would be the one♪

64
00:05:49,354 --> 00:05:54,430
♪I would rely on all my life♪

65
00:05:54,834 --> 00:05:58,670
♪What a joke♪

66
00:06:02,914 --> 00:06:05,398
♪Stop saying
love is the cure for loneliness♪

67
00:06:05,399 --> 00:06:05,999
Let go of me.

68
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:06,789
Let go.

69
00:06:06,790 --> 00:06:10,279
♪Stop calling the chaos
a fortress of joy♪

70
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:15,701
♪Is it you or is it me? Or is it
someone else who made the mistake?♪

71
00:06:15,702 --> 00:06:17,507
♪Say no more♪

72
00:06:17,508 --> 00:06:21,159
♪Even if I spend my entire life proving
love is in vain♪

73
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:24,398
♪Even if this was an inescapable fate♪

74
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:25,749
Lu Siyan.

75
00:06:26,565 --> 00:06:30,841
♪Could it be that this cycle of rebirth♪

76
00:06:30,948 --> 00:06:33,039
♪Is burning?♪

77
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,070
Lu Siyan.

78
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,470
Father, Mother,

79
00:06:47,879 --> 00:06:48,989
what brings you here?

80
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,869
Why are you alone?

81
00:06:58,920 --> 00:06:59,869
Should there be

82
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,318
someone else?

83
00:07:01,319 --> 00:07:02,429
I saw...

84
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:03,350
Father,

85
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:05,950
we got some client feedback

86
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,549
saying that the facial cleansing soap

87
00:07:07,639 --> 00:07:08,878
spoils too easily.

88
00:07:08,879 --> 00:07:09,719
I was thinking,

89
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,749
maybe we should add
another refinement step.

90
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,989
You know about that?

91
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,799
I did whatever job I could

92
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:17,950
to survive.

93
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:19,398
All right.

94
00:07:19,399 --> 00:07:20,398
You'll be in charge

95
00:07:20,399 --> 00:07:21,789
of this.

96
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:24,510
I'll have them move everything out.

97
00:07:24,879 --> 00:07:25,758
The few of you,

98
00:07:25,759 --> 00:07:27,030
move all this out.

99
00:07:27,279 --> 00:07:28,070
Hold on.

100
00:07:49,079 --> 00:07:50,350
(How could it be?)

101
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:11,989
What's wrong?

102
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,189
Nothing.

103
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,510
I saw it wrong.

104
00:08:23,839 --> 00:08:25,160
Mother, aren't you leaving yet?

105
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,470
You know what to do.

106
00:08:39,554 --> 00:08:40,550
Yes, Madam.

107
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:17,890
Siyan.

108
00:09:17,891 --> 00:09:19,030
Don't come near me.

109
00:09:22,679 --> 00:09:23,629
I'm worried about you.

110
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,710
Don't come closer.

111
00:09:29,399 --> 00:09:30,509
Are you okay, Siyan?

112
00:09:31,039 --> 00:09:32,749
Don't come near me.

113
00:09:33,211 --> 00:09:36,350
♪Barging into the sea
that bears your name♪

114
00:09:36,582 --> 00:09:38,479
♪Swimming to the end with loneliness♪

115
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,350
Siyan.

116
00:09:40,799 --> 00:09:41,989
Lin Chuning.

117
00:09:42,531 --> 00:09:45,944
♪Clearing the fog
just to get close to you♪

118
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:49,936
You're playing with fire.

119
00:09:49,937 --> 00:09:51,719
♪Wandering near your heart♪

120
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:53,070
Then,

121
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:55,029
let it burn brighter.

122
00:09:56,194 --> 00:09:57,833
♪So close, yet out of reach♪

123
00:09:57,834 --> 00:09:59,319
I gave you a chance.

124
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,918
You didn't listen.
Now you won't escape.

125
00:10:00,919 --> 00:10:02,310
Cut your crap.

126
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:06,149
What I want

127
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:08,210
is you doing this willingly.

128
00:10:08,211 --> 00:10:12,501
♪I was never part of your world♪

129
00:10:12,502 --> 00:10:16,107
♪If your silhouette
was etched upon the sea♪

130
00:10:16,108 --> 00:10:19,113
♪The sky as your wedding dress♪

131
00:10:19,114 --> 00:10:22,764
♪Turn me into a cloud♪

132
00:10:22,765 --> 00:10:25,747
♪Keep a sliver of the past♪

133
00:10:25,748 --> 00:10:28,398
♪If love is like an illusory bubble♪

134
00:10:28,399 --> 00:10:29,529
We can't do this.

135
00:10:29,530 --> 00:10:31,621
♪Together forever in my dreams♪

136
00:10:31,622 --> 00:10:33,030
This isn't right.

137
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:35,950
Leave.

138
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,029
Go.

139
00:10:37,257 --> 00:10:38,150
Just go.

140
00:10:45,799 --> 00:10:48,190
How do you know

141
00:10:53,159 --> 00:10:54,670
I'm not doing this willingly?

142
00:10:56,799 --> 00:10:58,590
Madam said you've lived too long.

143
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,430
Lin Chuning.

144
00:11:09,559 --> 00:11:10,590
You're hurt.

145
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:12,109
It's not my blood.

146
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:16,670
Madam,

147
00:11:17,679 --> 00:11:18,989
I failed.

148
00:11:19,279 --> 00:11:20,670
Useless fool.

149
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,790
Find somewhere to hide.

150
00:11:22,879 --> 00:11:24,029
Don't let anyone see you.

151
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:25,830
Yes, Madam.

152
00:11:32,017 --> 00:11:32,870
Cong,

153
00:11:33,074 --> 00:11:35,270
gather everyone in the household.

154
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:38,070
Check who has a wound on their chest.

155
00:11:38,519 --> 00:11:39,229
Yes.

156
00:11:39,719 --> 00:11:41,430
Even if we find him,
he's still a useless fool.

157
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:43,190
Can't even kill a woman.

158
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:44,599
Mother,

159
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:46,149
- do you know they...
- Shut up.

160
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,749
Lu Yijing,

161
00:11:48,039 --> 00:11:49,350
what were you trying to get at?

162
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:52,950
Send Ms. Yijing to the girls' school

163
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:54,470
to learn proper virtues.

164
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,239
Mother.

165
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,229
Go now.

166
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:57,199
Mother,

167
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,430
I don't want to go.

168
00:11:58,879 --> 00:12:00,319
Mother, it's my fault.

169
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:01,079
I don't want to go.

170
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:03,239
I don't want to go to the girls' school. Mother.

171
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:04,029
Mother,

172
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:06,109
Lu Yijing does need discipline,

173
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:08,670
but sending her to the girls' school
isn't necessary.

174
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:10,233
In this age,

175
00:12:10,234 --> 00:12:12,750
teaching girls all those outdated rules

176
00:12:12,771 --> 00:12:13,830
isn't good.

177
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:15,950
Are you going soft on her?

178
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,109
Of course not.

179
00:12:18,159 --> 00:12:19,190
Siyan,

180
00:12:19,679 --> 00:12:21,350
they're both your sisters.

181
00:12:21,519 --> 00:12:23,079
Please let her off this time.

182
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:24,350
Don't keep digging.

183
00:12:25,440 --> 00:12:26,269
Mother,

184
00:12:26,799 --> 00:12:28,269
are you saying

185
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:29,509
Yijing

186
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,350
tried to kill me?

187
00:12:32,159 --> 00:12:33,149
Chuning,

188
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:35,878
the girls' school will teach her well.

189
00:12:35,879 --> 00:12:37,269
She won't do that again.

190
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:38,710
All right.

191
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:41,190
Since you've said so,

192
00:12:41,519 --> 00:12:43,550
I'll let her off this time.

193
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:46,149
You're such a sweetheart.

194
00:12:46,279 --> 00:12:47,398
I'll sleep with you tonight.

195
00:12:47,399 --> 00:12:48,710
Let's have a nice chat.

196
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:50,590
Mother,

197
00:12:51,788 --> 00:12:53,270
I hope

198
00:12:53,474 --> 00:12:54,990
you'll protect Chuning

199
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:57,296
and don't let anyone hurt her.

200
00:12:57,297 --> 00:12:58,430
All right?

201
00:12:59,880 --> 00:13:00,910
Cong,

202
00:13:01,679 --> 00:13:02,638
stay outside

203
00:13:02,639 --> 00:13:04,398
Ms. Chuning's room tonight.

204
00:13:04,399 --> 00:13:06,950
If anything happens, just shoot.

205
00:13:07,879 --> 00:13:08,550
Yes.

206
00:13:28,759 --> 00:13:29,670
Anyone out there?

207
00:13:29,759 --> 00:13:30,749
Open the door.

208
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:48,909
Mochen,

209
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,470
you're finally here.

210
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:52,070
Jing,

211
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:53,190
are you all right?

212
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:56,350
I've knocked out the people
who locked you up.

213
00:13:57,360 --> 00:14:01,269
You don't have to go to the girls' school.
Stay at my place, and don't worry.

214
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:04,190
But...

215
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:06,830
If Mother finds out I'm not there

216
00:14:07,039 --> 00:14:09,710
and traces it back to you,
you'll be in trouble.

217
00:14:09,919 --> 00:14:11,229
Don't worry.

218
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:12,830
Just to be safe,

219
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:14,670
write a few letters to your family.

220
00:14:14,960 --> 00:14:17,560
I'll have someone send them
to the Lu Residence from time to time.

221
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:19,269
That way, your parents won't worry.

222
00:14:21,679 --> 00:14:22,509
All right.

223
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:25,790
You're always so kind to me.

224
00:14:30,919 --> 00:14:31,950
Chuning,

225
00:14:32,519 --> 00:14:34,470
all the girls in the town are here.

226
00:14:34,679 --> 00:14:35,959
Help me take a look.

227
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:37,109
See which girl is a good match.

228
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:38,470
Mother,

229
00:14:38,639 --> 00:14:39,869
what is this for?

230
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:42,430
I'm finding your brother a wife.

231
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:45,790
Ms. Li is good.

232
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:48,070
She's from a studious family,
and she's good looking, too.

233
00:14:48,679 --> 00:14:50,638
Ms. Zhang is also a good choice.

234
00:14:50,639 --> 00:14:53,470
She's gentle. She must fit your brother.

235
00:14:54,840 --> 00:14:55,989
Anyone you choose

236
00:14:56,159 --> 00:14:57,109
must be the best.

237
00:14:58,320 --> 00:15:00,149
You're already engaged yourself,

238
00:15:00,159 --> 00:15:01,950
your brother should settle down, too.

239
00:15:02,559 --> 00:15:05,950
As your mother, all I wish to see
is my children have their own families.

240
00:15:09,919 --> 00:15:10,599
Mother,

241
00:15:10,600 --> 00:15:11,430
what's wrong?

242
00:15:12,279 --> 00:15:13,989
I'm fine. Just the usual old ailment.

243
00:15:14,200 --> 00:15:15,470
When I start worrying,

244
00:15:15,559 --> 00:15:16,790
I have a headache.

245
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:20,479
Here's your temple.

246
00:15:20,480 --> 00:15:21,518
Let me massage it.

247
00:15:21,519 --> 00:15:22,950
It should relieve your pain.

248
00:15:24,799 --> 00:15:26,830
(She's a good child.)

249
00:15:27,360 --> 00:15:28,670
(What a pity.)

250
00:15:58,045 --> 00:15:58,999
How was your rest

251
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:00,389
last night?

252
00:16:01,611 --> 00:16:05,470
♪Then you turned away with your sleeves
drifting like clouds♪

253
00:16:06,030 --> 00:16:07,001
Not talking to me?

254
00:16:08,725 --> 00:16:10,398
If you're ignoring me,

255
00:16:10,399 --> 00:16:11,790
then I'll give you this.

256
00:16:12,320 --> 00:16:13,389
Hey.

257
00:16:15,759 --> 00:16:17,269
You'd better keep the flowers

258
00:16:17,400 --> 00:16:19,287
for your Ms. Li and Ms. Chen.

259
00:16:21,948 --> 00:16:22,941
Who are you talking about?

260
00:16:22,942 --> 00:16:24,964
♪All the love and grief♪

261
00:16:24,965 --> 00:16:26,450
♪Life brings♪

262
00:16:26,451 --> 00:16:27,800
The girls you've been set up with.

263
00:16:27,800 --> 00:16:31,301
♪Can't compared to young love's pain♪

264
00:16:31,302 --> 00:16:33,479
♪We met too late in this life♪

265
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:35,310
Are you jealous?

266
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:36,904
No.

267
00:16:37,760 --> 00:16:39,947
♪Even for a moment?♪

268
00:16:39,948 --> 00:16:42,289
♪In a dream, I searched in vain♪

269
00:16:42,290 --> 00:16:43,439
I don't care who Ms. Chen

270
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:44,590
or Ms. Zhang is.

271
00:16:44,879 --> 00:16:46,430
There's only one person in my heart.

272
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:47,470
Ms. Lin.

273
00:16:47,822 --> 00:16:50,372
♪You're the moon above the trees♪

274
00:16:50,519 --> 00:16:51,950
Once you and Xiaorou

275
00:16:52,240 --> 00:16:53,638
both return to your places,

276
00:16:53,639 --> 00:16:55,670
I'll tell my parents the truth.

277
00:16:56,400 --> 00:16:58,038
If you can't be their daughter,

278
00:16:58,039 --> 00:16:59,790
you can be their daughter-in-law.

279
00:17:00,542 --> 00:17:04,661
♪You took my hand
to ride beneath the stars♪

280
00:17:04,662 --> 00:17:06,639
♪You are the shore
where our stories crossed♪

281
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:08,510
But your mother loathes me,

282
00:17:08,559 --> 00:17:10,669
how would she ever accept me
as her daughter-in-law?

283
00:17:10,885 --> 00:17:12,879
♪On a solitary boat♪

284
00:17:12,880 --> 00:17:13,949
That doesn't matter.

285
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:16,719
I warned them last night.

286
00:17:16,720 --> 00:17:18,280
They wouldn't dare
to do anything anymore.

287
00:17:18,280 --> 00:17:22,120
♪You're the one I moon over♪

288
00:17:22,577 --> 00:17:23,790
What matters most is

289
00:17:24,319 --> 00:17:25,629
you're mine.

290
00:17:26,051 --> 00:17:27,470
As long as you accept me,

291
00:17:28,491 --> 00:17:29,350
that's all I need.

292
00:17:35,519 --> 00:17:37,270
I've talked to my father.

293
00:17:37,839 --> 00:17:40,709
The engagement banquet
will be held at Xianli Capital.

294
00:17:41,371 --> 00:17:43,439
I've been using my visits to Xiaorou

295
00:17:43,440 --> 00:17:46,709
to smear phosphorus powder
on that golden cage.

296
00:17:46,880 --> 00:17:50,149
Mr. Gao lets the peacock out
every evening.

297
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:51,669
When the time comes,

298
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:53,310
let's leave the rest to the peacock.

299
00:17:54,851 --> 00:17:56,710
Mr. Gao's good time

300
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:58,750
is soon ending.

301
00:18:04,068 --> 00:18:05,038
It's edible.

302
00:18:05,039 --> 00:18:05,869
Try it.

303
00:18:22,091 --> 00:18:22,950
Is it good?

304
00:18:27,759 --> 00:18:28,590
Try it.

305
00:18:36,702 --> 00:18:37,910
What I want

306
00:18:40,839 --> 00:18:42,149
isn't that.

307
00:18:49,960 --> 00:18:52,318
Chief Shen and Ms. Lu
really are a perfect match

308
00:18:52,319 --> 00:18:53,590
made in heaven.

309
00:19:03,720 --> 00:19:05,479
Mr. Gao and Mr. Siyan
have the same eyes.

310
00:19:05,480 --> 00:19:07,429
I can tell they're uncle and nephew.

311
00:19:08,880 --> 00:19:09,669
Really?

312
00:19:12,720 --> 00:19:14,629
Sharp eyes, ma'am.

313
00:19:15,440 --> 00:19:18,278
When a couple lives together
for a long time, they'll look alike.

314
00:19:18,279 --> 00:19:18,959
Not to mention,

315
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:20,598
Siyan and his uncle

316
00:19:20,599 --> 00:19:21,879
who have lived under the same roof

317
00:19:21,880 --> 00:19:23,389
for twenty years.

318
00:19:23,559 --> 00:19:24,758
It's only natural

319
00:19:24,759 --> 00:19:26,389
to have a resemblance.

320
00:19:30,799 --> 00:19:31,669
Father,

321
00:19:31,920 --> 00:19:33,070
I need to be somewhere else.

322
00:19:33,359 --> 00:19:34,429
I'll get going.

323
00:19:34,759 --> 00:19:35,750
Go on.

324
00:19:38,279 --> 00:19:40,278
Mr. Gao raises this peacock.

325
00:19:40,279 --> 00:19:41,518
It's beautiful.

326
00:19:41,519 --> 00:19:42,879
It is.

327
00:19:42,880 --> 00:19:44,598
I suppose he spent a fortune on this.

328
00:19:44,599 --> 00:19:45,709
Yeah.

329
00:19:51,640 --> 00:19:52,719
Fire!

330
00:19:52,720 --> 00:19:53,439
Fire!

331
00:19:53,440 --> 00:19:55,350
Fire! Run!

332
00:19:55,840 --> 00:19:57,035
- This way.
- This way.

333
00:19:59,559 --> 00:20:00,590
Move.

334
00:20:00,920 --> 00:20:03,189
Don't run away! Come back.

335
00:20:03,571 --> 00:20:04,799
- Get out of the way.
- Go.

336
00:20:04,800 --> 00:20:06,041
Excuse me.

337
00:20:06,260 --> 00:20:08,176
- Hurry up.
- Leave now.

338
00:20:08,177 --> 00:20:09,318
Fire!

339
00:20:09,319 --> 00:20:10,239
Fire!

340
00:20:10,240 --> 00:20:12,070
- Run!
- Run!

341
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:14,239
- Xianli Capital's in this kind of business.
- Fire!

342
00:20:14,240 --> 00:20:15,560
Put the fire out, everyone.

343
00:20:15,560 --> 00:20:16,873
It's on fire! Put the fire out.

344
00:20:16,874 --> 00:20:17,467
Siyan,

345
00:20:17,468 --> 00:20:19,590
go search for the ledger.
I'll look for Xiaorou.

346
00:20:19,891 --> 00:20:21,378
Fire?

347
00:20:22,720 --> 00:20:23,669
Xiaorou!

348
00:20:26,165 --> 00:20:27,647
Quick.

349
00:20:29,200 --> 00:20:30,230
Xiaorou!

350
00:20:32,799 --> 00:20:33,830
Xiaorou.

351
00:20:34,457 --> 00:20:35,473
Chuning.

352
00:20:35,474 --> 00:20:36,278
This way.

353
00:20:36,279 --> 00:20:36,879
I feel weak.

354
00:20:36,880 --> 00:20:37,840
I'll get you out of here.

355
00:20:37,840 --> 00:20:38,838
- Xiaorou.
- It's on fire.

356
00:20:38,839 --> 00:20:39,709
Found her.

357
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:40,949
Let's go.

358
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:44,080
Mr. Siyan, please get me out of here.

359
00:20:44,080 --> 00:20:46,278
- I don't want to die.
- Take Xiaorou and leave now. Quick.

360
00:20:46,279 --> 00:20:46,719
Mr. Siyan.

361
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:47,990
We should go together.

362
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:49,869
- I can't. I sprained my foot.
- Mr. Siyan.

363
00:20:50,119 --> 00:20:51,909
Stop dawdling, or we'll all die here.

364
00:20:52,119 --> 00:20:53,149
Take her and leave now.

365
00:20:53,800 --> 00:20:56,120
- Mr. Siyan, please get me out of here.
- Do as I say. Hurry.

366
00:20:56,319 --> 00:20:58,469
Remember. Don't go anywhere.
I'll be right back.

367
00:21:02,200 --> 00:21:03,149
Be careful.

368
00:21:30,100 --> 00:21:33,360
♪Barging into the sea
that bears your name♪

369
00:21:33,420 --> 00:21:35,989
♪Swimming to the end with loneliness♪

370
00:21:35,990 --> 00:21:39,389
♪Going against the current
and over the reef traps♪

371
00:21:39,390 --> 00:21:42,830
♪Clearing the fog
just to get close to you♪

372
00:21:43,460 --> 00:21:46,580
♪Pushing away the gravel
hidden beneath the seaweed♪

373
00:21:46,790 --> 00:21:49,299
♪Wandering near your heart♪

374
00:21:49,300 --> 00:21:53,009
♪I imagined
our encounter countless times♪

375
00:21:53,010 --> 00:21:56,180
♪So close, yet out of reach♪

376
00:21:56,740 --> 00:22:02,240
♪Keeping
all this lonely courage to myself♪

377
00:22:03,050 --> 00:22:09,309
♪I was never part of your world♪

378
00:22:09,310 --> 00:22:13,029
♪If your silhouette
was etched upon the sea♪

379
00:22:13,030 --> 00:22:15,949
♪The sky as your wedding dress♪

380
00:22:15,950 --> 00:22:19,679
♪Turn me into a cloud♪

381
00:22:19,680 --> 00:22:22,659
♪Keep a sliver of the past♪

382
00:22:22,660 --> 00:22:26,419
♪If love is like an illusory bubble♪

383
00:22:26,420 --> 00:22:29,749
♪Together forever in my dreams♪

384
00:22:29,750 --> 00:22:35,600
♪I'd rest forever in your arms♪

