389
00:23:03,460 --> 00:23:06,609
♪Returning to the land
Left bare by the receding sea♪

390
00:23:06,610 --> 00:23:09,379
♪Withering like a fallen leaf♪

391
00:23:09,380 --> 00:23:13,029
♪The message in a bottle
buried on the shore♪

392
00:23:13,030 --> 00:23:16,180
♪No one asked♪

